Notes

Limited to 2000 copies. Self released by the band and only sold at select record stores. Each copy was pressed on randomly colored vinyl so that no two look alike. Some copies were hand assembled and autographed by vocalist Wayne Coyne. Side one is 33RPM, side two is 45RPM. Recorded at Tarbox Road Studios, Wayne's House and Guillermo's Computer Published by Lovely Sorts of Death, BMI
